## Template 5: Convert Notes to Bug Report

Title: Generic Authentication Error Intercepts Basic Input Validation Flags
Environment: Windows / Web Browser
Severity: Medium
Steps to Reproduce:
1. Navigate to https://app.vwo.com
2. Enter explicitly invalid inputs (e.g. an invalid string format or HTML test payload)
3. Submit the form
Expected Result: Form should clearly delineate if an input is explicitly breaking formatting constraints before initiating credential checks against the DB.
Actual Result: Bypasses explicit field validation entirely to show a generic credential mismatch banner.
Evidence Required: Network tab export showing the API response payload.
